race.comment: FROSTY GIRL (9) exciting mare who continued where she left off last campaign when returning for an effortless victory over 1400m at Warwick Farm in weaker class. Has the upside to test these from the inside gate. Goes close. MAWJOOD (5) kept fresh after racing keenly early when a below par seventh in the Big Dance Qualifier over the 1600m at Randwick on October 18. Well placed back to the 1400m and Josh Parr won well on him two back at this track and trip. Value play. FORMAL DISPLAY (3) anchored with 60.5kg when a tough on-pace second over this trip at Warwick Farm. Will relish the claim and has top-three prospects. STARMAN (13) returns from a let-up and can surprise some of these if they overdo it up front. Kept up to the mark with a trial placing over 821m. Strays in the mix.
